title: China Palace
typeOfFood: Ovo, Chinese, Thai, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Asian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Chinese and Thai food. Staff know about the ingredients in each dish. Veg choices include the vegetable delight, braised tofu, ma po tofu, and Thai dishes such as curries, pad thai, pad see ew, vegetable fried rice. Be sure to specify no fish sauce (or egg), especially in the Thai dishes.
